{"tid":276271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"二哥想帶個野仔番屋企 (一人一個藉口)","createTime":"2017-06-08T16:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T22:22:13.000Z","uid":94964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"958d35de503cfe4d57bd1069129327eed93b0f6e","tid":276271,"uid":94964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:29:17.000Z","msg":"四年前， 我二哥係同佢老婆嘈交果陣， 二嫂返左佢娘家住左大半年， 其間兩個小朋都係由我屋企人照顧（二嫂不聞不聽）。  半年時間期間，我二哥係出面同第二個女人生左bb, 果個女人係佢前前度黎，當時我二哥堅持唔要個小朋友， 但結果佢都係生左出黎。<br />\n家陣個私生仔就黎三歲， 我二哥想接個私生子返去屋企養，  因為個前度話可以唔要名份，唔要錢，唔要小朋友（但要俾佢探個小朋友） 。 現在重點係唔可以俾二嫂知，同埋點同屋企人講？ <br />\n<br />\n背景資料： <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1: 二哥本身有兩個小朋友一個10歲， 一個三歲<br />\n<br />\n2: 二嫂係超級麻煩既人黎同埋好惡(未離婚) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"183086e06db36c0647f1fdca86ba786b9946fa8e","tid":276271,"uid":94964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4edc47193be639d985e4f9a8bd9a1862f6aa88db","tid":276271,"uid":50330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:37:26.000Z","msg":"帶野仔返屋企都可以有藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a0ef35cb49ca7f5933afd4e2bb84f2c97e3e45","tid":276271,"uid":94964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:38:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶野仔返屋企都可以有藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係唔想家變 想集思廣益"},{"pid":"d93b9ece21e80d740eca39fd34062cb3028a47e8","tid":276271,"uid":74096,"l